## ğŸ“Œ Project Overview
This project is a **fully functional and responsive developer portfolio website**
built using **Java, Spring Boot, Thymeleaf, and Bootstrap 5**.

The portfolio is designed to showcase technical skills, real-world projects,
and GitHub work in a **recruiter-friendly and professional manner**.

The project strictly follows the **Software Development Life Cycle (SDLC)**,
simulating real-world engineering practices.

